{"tid":378590,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女子偶像握手會慘變惡臭會！官方終推動體臭對策","createTime":"2017-08-28T15:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T15:26:59.000Z","uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9cda89a808020eade5645c0915b907b6ed5b535","tid":378590,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:18:55.000Z","msg":"AKB48出道自今，以「可見面的偶像」為活動宗旨，出道後舉行的「握手會」多如繁星，而其他姐妹團亦同樣仿效，定期舉辦握手會。<br />\n<br />\n不過早前SKE48在宣傳新單曲《意外にマンゴー》（中譯：意外的芒果），從7月至今連續舉行多次握手會中，卻發生了一個小播曲。成員松村香織在Twitter上發表了一篇推文「儘管很感謝大家來參加活動，但有女粉絲覺得會場的味道讓她受不了。因為自己是聞不到自身的味道，所以請大家多多注意自己的體味，如果有需要可以到藥房購買以下商品哦」。<br />\n<br />\n之後那位女粉絲亦在自己的Twitter中發文「是我說的，雖然不是每個人都很臭，但是真的有那種臭到讓人受不了的人，特別排隊動彈不得時更無比難受，就像被關在盛夏的男生社團房中」。<br />\n<br />\n在炎夏中舉辦握手會，細小場館中擠了一大堆人，經已不單是汗流浹背，尤其有些人流汗後散發的氣味，光想想也知那味道的程度是很恐怖，而這段小插曲也備受各大媒體及粉絲間熱話。<br />\n<br />\n官方有見及此，終於決定出手，在握手會場中設立一角「淨化間」，提供多種消毒除臭用道供參加者使用。看來也是用品商看見這個宣傳商機而作出的舉動呢！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://japhub.com/?c=5985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D5985&d=GJF458Ascgpdq%2BHFbQ4yEy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=25f8c9e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://japhub.com/?c=5985</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/231848_449ca121c3f3d9a39d60729d8bbbbbc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F231848_449ca121c3f3d9a39d60729d8bbbbbc4.jpg&h=1394380d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15b7e61e2b757ddb9b449ce96c2fec222c18c7ce","tid":378590,"uid":66779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:21:30.000Z","msg":"毒撚畀錢畀人撚 慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過某啲係幾臭 抵撚"},{"pid":"ab6319f0c8f3ea034b181d238dd76d006fe4b0fe","tid":378590,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:23:24.000Z","msg":"一堆劇毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4a07619e75547aabb3383c5dda656139f9dff3","tid":378590,"uid":20943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:23:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚畀錢畀人撚 慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過某啲係幾臭 抵撚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c6049ace1ce91b4aac1fb716165ba049ca7889","tid":378590,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:26:03.000Z","msg":"點淨化都冇用，已經毒到入骨。"},{"pid":"e4a8f9f03dfdfe830ab4af0ebd0336653c3bd7c0","tid":378590,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"毒氣衝天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9639936d6be1fddbadc26d42af47d4058b8bc4","tid":378590,"uid":7140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚畀錢畀人撚 慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過某啲係幾臭 抵撚</blockquote><br />\n肥柒臭油頭毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}